  "text": "1 O 2 has a short halftime of about 200 ns in cells [CITATION_1] , and reacts with target molecules in the immediate neighbourhood. The possible diffusion distance of 1 O 2 has been calculated to be up to 10 nm in a physiologically relevant situation [CITATION_2] .",
